msgid ""
"Most dynamic interface types write their current gateway into a file "
"named :code:`/tmp/[interface]_router` or "
":code:`/tmp/[interface]_routerv6`. When the expected gateway is not "
"listed in the page, there might be an issue with the interface type (for "
"example the remote server isn't providing one at the moment)."
msgstr ""

